name: All this time that I've wasted
description: The storm seems to be growing. It's making it harder to breathe. It must be the heat wave. Someone blew out the candles. So it goes with time imitating some kind of universal ripple. Am I still alive? I hear the ocean. The ocean tells me I cant breathe. I really need some air. I took the keys with me. How would you know? Someone has to be there when it is needed most.
